==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Court-cupboard
<hw>Court"-cup`board</hw> <pr>(-k?b`b?rd)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A movable sideboard or buffet, on which plate and other articles of luxury were displayed on special occasions.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A way with the joint stools, remove the <qex>court-cupboard</qex>, look to the plate.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Courteous</ent>⟦br⟧
